Arithmetic Operators:
*, +,-,/,%
Assignment Operator:
       int x=10;
        int y;
        y=x-- - --x + ++x - --x;
         y=x-- - x-- + ++x - x--;
         y=x-- + x++ + ++x - x-- - --x;
         y=++x - --x + ++x - x++;
         y=++x - ++x - ++x - ++x;

Statements in java
1. Expression Statement : x=y+z
2. Declaration Statements : int x=10;
3. Control Statements